.SH SHELL COMPLETIONS
Loaded for: kubectl, docker, mise, gh, rustup, cargo, gcloud, fzf, yazi.
.SH SHELL OPTIONS
.TP
.B auto_cd
Type a directory name to cd into it (e.g.,
.B ../foo
instead of
.BR "cd ../foo" ).
.TP
.B extended_glob
Advanced glob patterns (#, ~, ^).
.TP
.B correct
Suggests corrections for mistyped commands.
.TP
.B share_history
Share history across all open shells.
.TP
.B hist_ignore_dups
Skip duplicate history entries.
.TP
.B hist_ignore_space
Commands starting with a space are not recorded.
.SH GIT CONFIG
Managed via stow at
.BR ~/.gitconfig .
Machine-specific overrides go in
.BR ~/.gitconfig.local .
.PP
Key settings:
.TP
.B core.pager
delta (with navigate mode)
.TP
.B commit.gpgSign
SSH signing via 1Password (op-ssh-sign)
.TP
.B core.excludesfile
~/.gitignore (stow-managed global gitignore)
.TP
.B push.autoSetupRemote
Auto-track upstream on first push
.TP
.B fetch.prune
Remove stale remote-tracking branches
.TP
.B filter.lfs
Git LFS enabled
.SH RUNTIMES
Managed by
.BR mise .
Versions in
.BR ~/.config/mise/config.toml :
node 22, python 3.13, ruby 3.4, go 1.24.
Rust managed via
.BR rustup .
.SH THEME
Catppuccin Mocha everywhere: Ghostty, Zellij (zjstatus), Starship, Zed,
Yazi, bat, lazygit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.B ~/Workspace/mac-setup/
Repository root
.TP
.B ~/config-backups/
Timestamped backups from bootstrap runs
.TP
.B ~/.gitconfig.local
Machine-specific git config (user.email, credential helpers)
.TP
.B ~/.ssh/config
1Password SSH agent config (stow-managed), includes config.local
.TP
.B ~/.ssh/config.local
Machine-specific SSH hosts (not tracked)
.TP
.B ~/.secrets
Machine-specific env vars (not tracked)
.TP
.B ~/.local/state/zsh/history
Zsh history file (50k lines)
.SH COMMON TASKS
.TP
.B Re-run bootstrap
./setup.sh
.TP
.B Dry run
./setup.sh \-\-dry\-run
.TP
.B Re-stow a package
(cd stow && stow \-\-target="$HOME" \-\-restow git)
.TP
.B Update runtimes
Edit stow/mise/.config/mise/config.toml, then mise install
.TP
.B Add a Homebrew package
Add to brew/Brewfile, then brew bundle \-\-file=brew/Brewfile
.TP
.B Run tests
bats tests/
.TP
.B Export Zed extensions
\&./scripts/export-zed-extensions.sh
.TP
.B Manage skip-worktree
\&./scripts/skip-worktree.sh \-\-help
